           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Fincatura : Linea 17                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      17                   to   v-lin                  .
