      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Routine di conversione da altra valuta a valuta base      *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : w-cvs-vlt-sgl = Sigla dell'altra valuta          *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-dec = Numero decimali dell'altra valu- *
      *    *                          ta                               *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-tdc = Tipo di coefficiente dell'altra  *
      *    *                          valuta                           *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-cdc = Coefficiente di cambio dell'al-  *
      *    *                          tra valuta                       *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-aav = Ammontare da convertire, espres- *
      *    *                          so nell'altra valuta             *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Output : w-cvs-vlt-avb = Ammontare convertito, espresso   *
      *    *                          nella valuta base                *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
      *    * Routine di conversione da valuta base ad altra valuta     *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : w-cvs-vlt-sgl = Sigla dell'altra valuta          *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-dec = Numero decimali dell'altra valu- *
      *    *                          ta                               *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-tdc = Tipo di coefficiente dell'altra  *
      *    *                          valuta                           *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-cdc = Coefficiente di cambio dell'al-  *
      *    *                          tra valuta                       *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-avb = Ammontare da convertire, espres- *
      *    *                          so nella valuta base             *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Output : w-cvs-vlt-aav = Ammontare convertito, espresso   *
      *    *                          nell'altra valuta                *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
      *    * Routine di conversione da valuta a valuta                 *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : Valuta da trasformare                            *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *            - w-cvs-vdt-sgl = Sigla valuta                 *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *            - w-cvs-vdt-dec = Numero decimali              *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *            - w-cvs-vdt-tdc = Tipo di coefficiente         *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *            - w-cvs-vdt-cdc = Coefficiente di cambio ri-   *
      *    *                              spetto alla valuta base      *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *            - w-cvs-vdt-amm = Ammontare da convertire,     *
      *    *                              espresso nella valuta da     *
      *    *                              trasformare                  *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          Valuta in cui trasformare                        *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *            - w-cvs-vnu-sgl = Sigla valuta                 *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *            - w-cvs-vnu-dec = Numero decimali              *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *            - w-cvs-vnu-tdc = Tipo di coefficiente         *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *            - w-cvs-vnu-cdc = Coefficiente di cambio ri-   *
      *    *                              spetto alla valuta base      *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Output : Valuta in cui trasformare                        *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *            - w-cvs-vnu-amm = Ammontare convertito,        *
      *    *                              espresso nella valuta        *
      *    *                              in cui trasformare           *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "swd/std/prg/cpy/wcvsvlt0.cps"                   .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Scrittura movimento di CGE                                *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       wrt-mov-cge-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Record [bit] da 'w-rig'                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-rec-bit        to   rf-bit                 .
       wrt-mov-cge-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione link-area testata e riga movi-  *
      *              * mento per programma di generazione movimenti di *
      *              * CGE                                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "NO"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Chiamata modulo '300z'                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cll-300-zet-000      thru cll-300-zet-999        .
       wrt-mov-cge-080.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura testata e prima riga movimento : riga *
      *              * 'cassa'                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "WR"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           move      rf-bit-dat-doc       to   l-cge-300-dat-reg      .
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-num-prt      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Forzatura del valore per la causale conta-  *
      *                  * bile                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      480                  to   l-cge-300-cod-cau      .
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-des-cau      .
           move      "N"                  to   l-cge-300-snx-dts      .
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-dat-sca      .
           move      rf-bit-dat-doc       to   l-cge-300-dat-doc      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione numero documento               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      06                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      rf-bit-num-doc (6:6) to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   l-cge-300-num-doc      .
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-cod-num      .
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-prt-iva      .
           move      w-buf-pdc-cas        to   l-cge-300-cod-pdc      .
           move      "G"                  to   l-cge-300-tip-arc      .
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-cod-arc      .
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-com-rig      .
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-dat-rif      .
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-num-rif      .
           move      "D"                  to   l-cge-300-dar-ave      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Totale documento                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bit-iva-tdo       to   l-cge-300-imp-mov      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * In presenza di sconto pagamento, il totale  *
      *                  * del documento viene diminuito del relativo  *
      *                  * importo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tot-arr        not  = zero
                     subtract  w-rig-tot-arr
                                          from l-cge-300-imp-mov      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Chiamata modulo '300z'                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cll-300-zet-000      thru cll-300-zet-999        .
       wrt-mov-cge-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura riga movimento : 'cliente'            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione link-area sola riga         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "N+"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           perform   cll-300-zet-000      thru cll-300-zet-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura sola riga                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "W+"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-cod-pdc      .
           move      "C"                  to   l-cge-300-tip-arc      .
           move      rf-bit-cod-arc       to   l-cge-300-cod-arc      .
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-com-rig      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se nelle righe bolla e' presente un nu- *
      *                      * mero documento si pone come riferimento *
      *                      * per la registrazione                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-buf-dat-rif          .
           move      spaces               to   w-buf-num-rif          .
       wrt-mov-cge-150.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Start su righe documento            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "SK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "NUMPRT    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      "NL"                 to   f-cfr                  .
           move      rf-bit-num-prt       to   rf-bir-num-prt         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-bir-num-prg         .
           move      "pgm/bol/fls/ioc/obj/iofbir"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-bir                 .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se Start errata : uscita        *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-500.
       wrt-mov-cge-200.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Lettura sequenziale archivio [bir]  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/bol/fls/ioc/obj/iofbir"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-bir                 .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se fine file : uscita           *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-500.
       wrt-mov-cge-300.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Max su archivio [bir]               *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bir-num-prt       not  = rf-bit-num-prt
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-500.
       wrt-mov-cge-400.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Bufferizzazione data e numero fat-  *
      *                          * tura                                *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bir-fat-dat       to   w-buf-dat-rif          .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Editing                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      06                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      rf-bir-fat-num (6:6) to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-buf-num-rif          .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Alla prima riga buona incontrata si *
      *                          * esce                                *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     wrt-mov-cge-500.
       wrt-mov-cge-500.
           move      w-buf-dat-rif        to   l-cge-300-dat-rif      .
           move      w-buf-num-rif        to   l-cge-300-num-rif      .
           move      "A"                  to   l-cge-300-dar-ave      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Totale documento                    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bit-iva-tdo       to   l-cge-300-imp-mov      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Chiamata modulo '300z'                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cll-300-zet-000      thru cll-300-zet-999        .
       wrt-mov-cge-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura eventuale riga : sconto pagamento     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su sconto pagamento                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tot-arr        =    zero
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione link-area sola riga         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "N+"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           perform   cll-300-zet-000      thru cll-300-zet-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura sola riga                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "W+"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .           
           move      w-buf-pdc-scp        to   l-cge-300-cod-pdc      .
           move      "G"                  to   l-cge-300-tip-arc      .
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-cod-arc      .
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-com-rig      .
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-dat-rif      .
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-num-rif      .
           move      "D"                  to   l-cge-300-dar-ave      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sconto pagamento                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-tot-arr        to   l-cge-300-imp-mov      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Chiamata modulo '300z'                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cll-300-zet-000      thru cll-300-zet-999        .
       wrt-mov-cge-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     wrt-mov-cge-999.
       wrt-mov-cge-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Routine di chiamata programma 'pcge300z'                  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cll-300-zet-000.
           move      "pgm/cge/prg/obj/pcge300z"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-cge-300              .
       cll-300-zet-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Subroutines per allineamenti a destra o a sinistra oppure *
      *    * al centro di campi alfanumerici di varia lunghezza, fi-   *
      *    * no ad un massimo di 240 caratteri, oppure per il conca-   *
      *    * tenamento, con o senza separazione, di max 10 substrin-   *
      *    * ghe in una unica substringa                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "swd/std/prg/cpy/wallstr0.cps"                   .

